data.title: Mergers And Acquisitions
data.meta_description: Merger & Acquisition - Free download as Word Doc (.doc / .docx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read online for free. Cisco Systems is a global leader in networking founded in 1984. It has annual revenues of $46 billion and over 66,000 employees worldwide. Cisco focuses on routing, switching, and other networking technologies and invests $4.5 billion annually in R&D. In India, Cisco has over 8,700 employees and leads the networking market in core technologies as well as wireless and security.
